rows.label: tlk41700122_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Have you tried those Nopon Radishes
Nomon makes? They're exquisite.

rows.label: tlk41700122_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Sometimes I feel a bit guilty slicing
them, with how they're shaped and all,
but it's actually good stress relief too!

rows.label: tlk41700122_05_msg0003
rows.name:
And at the end of the day, that
taste is just the best. They're a
quality product inside and out.

rows.label: tlk41700122_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I made the right decision, lending
my field out to that Nopon.
